{"tid":1717260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真黃店定偽黃店？希望各位可以答答我","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:15:30.000Z","uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d48bb5a14e24d17eb72753039820807d8bce1279","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"代手足po：<br />\n事因我就係呢間舖嘅員工，我就睇唔過眼呢間野扮黃，又整個連儂牆，又揾人幫佢地洗白話之前有罷工，但係所謂休息一日只係怕無生意而唔開門，而唔係支持整個運動，老闆同老闆娘又要撐警曱又要開住個cctvb，話啲黑衣人整塞條路，我唔洗揸車返黎開舖啦。<br />\n已經有個手足比佢發現去發夢而炒左，宜家三大罷又唔肯罷，1111到1113照開門<br />\n我宜家就趕住去旺角食糖水，希望大家唔好再去懲罰佢地，因為係唔撚值得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefa9b8047054ac1c8b0178817bfa45305bdbaef","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"我唔想再有藍扮黃嘅舖頭出現"},{"pid":"4cf00a4ddf66eb114efc1a016c3fcfd4a8a2df14","tid":1717260,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"249bd23ddf7c4115155fa06fab5052f456707a89","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"02173854f54fb9a45c8ccd50b0080d7e4dc71525","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"十連挑戰"},{"pid":"6a38929f50d8d7f07024df1a4b1297262ee66703","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9eeffbfdc07637325140dd989b29c9e08bcdb0a5","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b619d8e319604c6edbfd9cf1b55e6b4ee484c3","tid":1717260,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c